Montess Ivette Enjema (a mụrụ na Julaị 20, 1991) nke a maara nke ọma site na aha egwu ya bụ Montess, bụ onye na-agụ egwu, onye na-agba egwu na onye na-ede egwu na Cameroon. Ọ malitere ọrụ ya mgbe ọ dị afọ isii dịka onye na-agba egwú na Government Primary School Buea Town

O mechara ghọọ onye na-agba egwú ebe e nyere ya onye na- ịgba egwú kacha mma na obodo Buea n'oge asọmpi inter schools 11 February. Ọ ghọrọ onye a ma ama n'afọ 2015 mgbe ọ wepụtara "Love Witta Gun Man", abụ nke mere ka o nweta onyinye Afrima maka Best Female artiste na Central Africa n'afọ 2017.
